data.description: PRISTINE!  Built in 2021 & shows like a model. This ultra immaculate 2BR+Loft/2.5 BA two story Townhome is a showpiece, w/minimal use since purchase. Open concept allows you to cook & entertain all together. Shiny quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances & neutral cabinetry adorn the kitchen where you will feel right at home. Convenient powder room on 1st floor. Easy to maintain tile flooring downstairs w/carpet upstairs in both BR's & Loft. Impact windows, energy saving appliances, gated community & LOW HOA! Arbor Parc offers Pool, Fitness Center & Clubhouse including a Catering Kitchen for entertaining. Close to Shopping, Dining, Gardens Mall, Kravis Center, Norton Museum, I-95, FL Turnpike, PBI Airport & MORE!
